results.title: Skeleton Live, Laugh, Love meme, embroidered fabric face mask, washable, cotton, embroidered, reversible, elastic, headties, filter pocket
results.description:
This mask is embroidered on both sides. 1 side has Skeletor, the other has the words Live,Laugh,Love. 

The mask itself is made from lightweight, double-layered cotton blended fabric.  The pattern is embroidered onto the mask itself so unlike heat transfer patterns you can throw this in the wash without worrying about losing any of the detail of the design. 

The elastic bands are 11 inches long and are knotted at 9 inches. Adjusting the elastic is very simple. If you find it too long, you can rotate the elastic to expose the knot and then add an additional knot to shorten. If you need to lengthen it, you will need to undo the knot and retie it slightly higher up the elastic.

Head wrap ties are two strands of 3foot long cotton tshirt tubing fabric. To secure tie the top two above your ears and behind your head, and the bottom two bellow the base of your skull behind your head. 

We also have soft silicone adjustable loops available that will allow you to tighten or loosen the ear loops easily.

If you need something specific for your needs please feel free to let us know and we'll be happy to try and accommodate!

*****This product is made to order.****** 


Care Instructions:

Machine Wash warm with like colors.
Tumble dry low
Iron on medium heat as needed using a piece of cotton over embroidered pattern to avoid damage.

*****
Due to Covid-19
Shipping times may take longer than usual, especially overseas. Please check your tracking number for updates. 

No returns accepted on Face masks over embroidered pattern to avoid damage.
